text: Newfane High School is a New York State public high school located in Newfane, New York, United States. The senior high school's mascot is the panther. The Newfane School District was looking for a new assistant principal at the start of the 2017–2018 school year but has since hired Mrs. Danielle Hawkins. ==References== 3)^ http://newfane.wnyric.org/domain/5 3)^ http://newfane.wnyric.org/domain/34 Category:Public high schools in New York (state) Category:Schools in Niagara County, New York
